relation: Great for these types of students
Very safe there are police everywhere and they are easy to contact if you need help.
There are a lot of things to do at the school depending on what you are interested in.
great for any student! Especially people who cannot afford to go to a university.
Very cheap but good classes and teachers. Bogfee waiver is easy to get if you qualify for it
Go to the quad and you will find a lot of your friends. A lot of things going on in the middle of the school year, i am told, outside.
Cafeteria is really nice. There is a small student store for a little snack. There are vending machines around campus if you get thirsty.
Have not attended a class yet.
Do not procrastinate for ANYTHING. Do everything you need to right when you can do it and get it over with. It will help you into classes you need and finish faster.
At Cosumnes River College it is easy to talk to someone in the counciling office. It has a small campus. It is hard to get into the classes you want
